      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) operates under an ISO 9001-certified quality management system. Version control, regression testing, and release notes are documented. Achieved Gradation 3: full QMS with automated regression suite covering blood-pump relevant benchmarks."
    },
    {
