      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level of 2 for MRL 3.",
      "rationale": "Code verification performed against the Taylor-Green vortex manufactured solution and the ASME V&V 20 lid-driven cavity benchmark. Order-of-accuracy confirmation (second-order spatial convergence) documented. Achieved Gradation 3: independent third-party verification report available."
