    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors have been formally assessed and meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 3. The equivalency of input parameters factor was not formally assessed; the team judged this acceptable on the basis that simulation inputs are drawn directly from the validation test matrix. All other V&V activities are complete, validation error is within the 10% acceptance threshold, and the relative hemolysis index predictions satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five operating points. The package is accepted for submission to support the 510(k) predicate comparison.",
